Ok, here's an alternative version of the cartoon movie &quot;The Phantom Pollbooth&quot; from 1970. There's another 2.08 GB version available on TPB and a 572 MB re-encode of the same file as a separate torrent. Those two torrents are basically the same version but with different filesizes. So, I thought I would share my version which is also a VHS rip but with better sound and video quality, though the upper 1 cm part of the video is warped ... VHS tape symptom.

The rip contains a warning and some trailers at the beginning of the video which I didn't bother ripping. If you want to get rid of those you can use VirtualDub yourself. I'm seeding the original file as I got it from the great CG community.

